<%= error_messages_for 'dyno_image' %>
<%= hidden_field 'dyno_image', 'dyno_page_id'  %>

<!--[form:dyno_image]-->
<p><label for="dyno_image_caption">Caption</label>
<%= text_field 'dyno_image', 'caption'  %></p>

<p>Use thumb for news items.</p>
<p><label for="dyno_image_thumb">Thumb <%= link_to 'view', '/images'+url_for_file_column('dyno_image', 'thumb') if url_for_file_column('dyno_image', 'thumb') %></label>
<%= file_column_field 'dyno_image', 'thumb'  %></p>

<p>Sizes are as follows. Home page images need to be 974px by 529px.  All other pages should be 569px by 529px. </p>
<p><label for="dyno_image_image">Image <%= link_to 'view', '/images'+url_for_file_column('dyno_image', 'image') if url_for_file_column('dyno_image', 'image') %></label>
<%= file_column_field 'dyno_image', 'image'  %></p>
<!--[eoform:dyno_image]-->
